        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1586599132
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You need more than <code>tauto</code> to instantiate it because the proofs a&lt;= X  and b&lt;=X which will need might be themselves proved using linarith</p>",
        "id": 193652456,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1586599198
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>There is something here which always feels accessible to me, but which I don't quite understand properly.</p>",
